channel.description: Everyone knows that i have to compile my server before it edits...... but i keep getting the u do not have JDK 5.0 6.0 crap everyone has seen this before... how do i fix it comon guys i know everyone out there that is able to edit their server knows...

item.title: Compiler help
item.dc:creator: @sp3c sp3c
item.description:
@sp3c wrote:

Ok first off do u have jdk 6 update 2 or jdk 5 update 2? If you dont then search for it and download it, if u do, i had the same problem, make sure the file is named jdk1.6.0_02 or for jdk 5 update 2 make sure its named jdk1.5.0_02. That fixed my problem with the compiler error, i had jdk 6 named something else.
